{"tid":1817963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都係度諗自己有咩心願","createTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T16:05:07.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8bdc9b3b88b3cfbfb4247ea5240cf24ea07503","tid":1817963,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"係街見到d條件好好既人<br />\n又唔抵得<br />\n但都已經唔緊要<br />\n人越大越唔理人<br />\n係唔理得人咁多<br />\n你理人地<br />\n邊個理你<br />\n<br />\n其實自己有咩心願<br />\n問心<br />\n時間始終會過<br />\n始終要過<br />\n幾唔如意都好<br />\n芸芸眾生<br />\n其實真係冇太多意義可言<br />\n生老病死<br />\n<br />\n或者真係唔好諗太多<br />\n諗得多未必做到<br />\n做到又點<br />\n都係一步步咁行<br />\n你唔行<br />\n時間都推你行"},{"pid":"c7fe8c2d827fa2d062d17fd8cf2d8fc1fa89748d","tid":1817963,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50218edd18f2a3a41bcb00f178bbe373fa7668c","tid":1817963,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=44a77775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"f5d11fe85ba646f6625e67c443efaccf7e37eab1","tid":1817963,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"有時諗幾耐都諗唔到<br />\n做下其他野反而又會諗到少少"}]}